snippet.title: Garfield Lasagna Party - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
You're invited by Garfield, Odie, Arlene and Nermal's to their new purr-fect celebration: a huge Lasagna Party! And guess what's on the menu? A dynamic party game filled with crazy (and tasty!) mini games: pizza square slicing challenge, snowballs throwing competition, obstacle race and more!

Garfield (C) Paws Inc / Viacom International
Developed by Balio Studio
Published by Microids
Also available on PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S and Nintendo Switch
